name: Tropical Voyage
description:
The natural look and feel of Tropical Voyage adds just right amount flair to any outfit!! The possibilities are endless with all the color combinations these earrings can be worn with. So use your imagination and go wild!!

These earrings are made of acai beads and tagua nuts, natural beads from the tropical rainforests in South America. So in addition to being super chic, these earrings are also eco-friendly!!  

Note: The earrings you receive will vary in color than what is pictured here, according to available stock.

name: Eye Of The Tiger
description:
Tiger Eye is believed to have great healing powers and can develop courage and confidence. This grounding stone is also said to promote prosperity, clarity and protection. 

The tiger eye bead is accented with the Crystallized Swarovski Elements double twist gold spacers.

This bracelet fits a 7" to 7.5" wrist.

name: Breast Cancer Awareness
description:
The name says it all...let's black it out!! I will be adding new bracelets to in an effort to raise cancer awareness. As some may know, I have lost too many close loved ones to cancer. My mother and aunt have fought Breast Cancer and won. These bracelets are a stylish way to show your support and a portion of the proceeds will be donated towards Relay For Life 2013


These bracelets are sized to fit 7" to 7.5" wrist. If you need a smaller/larger size, please contact me BEFORE ordering.

name: "I AM"
description:
In the Old Testament, the Hebrew name for "God" was considered so holy that the people wouldn't even say it. So, when God appeared to Moses in the burning bush and sent him to lead the Israelites out of captivity, Moses asked God, "Who should I say sent me?" After all, he couldn't breathe the name of God in public. God replied by saying, "Moses, my name is I Am." In other words, "I am anything and everything you need. I am your joy. I am your peace. I am your strength. I am your victory. I am your way of escape. I am whatever you need."

Made with hematite beads and accented with black crystal rondelles and sideway rhinestone cross.

This bracelet is fits 7"-7.5" wrist. Please contact me if you need a bigger size before ordering.
